io.doov.core.dsl.path

Interface FieldPath

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultFieldPath

    public interface FieldPath
    Contains the same information as the Path annotation. Field paths are used for associating a field with a FieldId without using annotations. This is used at code generation for generating FieldInfo class.
